reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice and compact!
reviews.reviewText: Bought this to replace my previous cord keeper bag from a different company. This bag has all I need, and more! reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Nice but missing something
reviews.reviewText: This was wonderful to put all of my charging cords in. Was a bit easy to keep organized but could use spots for the bricks. There is a little pocket below the spot for cords but not big enough for a brick to go in. Happy with purchase but would not purchase again. This did hold up well for use on the trip, in airports, and on the plane. But once it does get worn out I will look for a different option.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great product at a great price!
reviews.reviewText: Getting ready for a summer cruise and needed to add this great organizer to my “must have” items. It matches the makeup bag I just bought. They are both quality products and will go very well with my new silver grey luggage!
It looks nice and I love the material but I think could be better if some of the spaces were a little bit bigger. Is hard to fit the cubes from the chargers in the spaces available
I have a smart house so I have sooooo many chargers laying everywhere. This helped me organize them and I use it when I travel! Highly recommend

reviews.reviewTitle: Dimensions parfaites pour les voyages. Beau produit de qualité.
reviews.reviewText: Absolument parfait pour transporter tout ce qu'il me faut pour partir en voyage sans être encombrant: iPad mini, câbles, batterie externe et chargeurs. À ma grande surprise, mon iPad mini est entré même avec son étui. C"est juste mais ça rentre sans mettre de pression sur les fermetures éclairs.Ce petit sac de rangement est très bien fait. Tout est de qualité dans ce produit: le tissu est tissé serré et les fermetures éclairs sont bien cousues et invisibles. Fait pour survivre à des années de manutention.Je recommande fortement ce produit.

I really love this product because you can put an iPad in it and all the cords needed and it is compact and the fact that it is waterproof is great in case something gets spilled on it and will be used to travel with and that way nothing gets lost. I don't know about the durability yet as it will be used for day trips every now and then but I think it will come in handy and recommend it!!
It is a bag to put cables in! It works.
